data.description: Your own piece of paradise in a private community with agricultural land where you can own horses and cattle. Peace River Acreage is a private gated community, with a private boat ramp for your convenience. Relax by your tranquil pond. This property has a master gate to beautiful, tranquil Peace River Community. Private gate to property, house with long front porch, pond view, mudroom, great room, loft overlooking first level   Pole barn. Lots of acreage and wildlife.  Nice lookout tower.     The property was damaged by hurricane Ian.--affected drywall, floors, cabinets and appliances were removed.  Flooring and drywall need to be replaced.  Kitchen was completely torn out.  Debris needs to be removed.  Home is being sold AS IS.  Priced accordingly.
